Dialogue: 7,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.66,Gen_Main_Up,,0,0,0,,Ver tu cara empeora mis náuseas.
Dialogue: 7,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.04,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Qué asco das, qué asco de voz.\NNo eres nadie.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.21,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(323.784,78.464)}m 0 0 l 210 0 210 50 0 50
