Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(176.707,228.002)}m 0 0 l 210 0 210 50 0 50
Dialogue: 2,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\c&H353B4E&\pos(183.428,232.527)}Sanbonsen\N{\b0}¿No te da vergüenza estar viva?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(72.707,127.079)}m 0 0 l 275 0 275 75 0 75
