Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(336.092,197.848)}m 0 0 l 305 0 305 90 0 90
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\c&H353B4E&\pos(342.198,202.989)}RINRIN\N{\b0}¿Creías que te lo perdonarían si te disculpabas?\NTe golpearía si te viera por ahí.\NPero me disculparé, así que perdóname, ¿sí?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(336.092,85.848)}m 0 0 l 270 0 270 60 0 60
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\c&H353B4E&\pos(342.198,89.758)}Pa\N{\b0}Desaparecer sería su única opción posible.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(30.861,82.771)}m 0 0 l 220 0 220 40 0 40
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\b0\c&H353B4E&\pos(39.429,89.758)}Deja el país, eres una vergüenza.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad0\p1\bord1\blur0.3\an7\fscx93\fscy74\c&HFDFEFD&\3c&H15192B&\pos(176.092,43.386)}m 0 0 l 243 0 243 40 0 40
Dialogue: 4,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.04,Cart_C_Ari,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs14\bord0\b0\c&H353B4E&\pos(181.583,50.989)}Todos se alegrarían si desaparecieras.
